---
title: Creamy Double Chorizo Linguine with Peas, Rocket and Balsamic Glaze
description: This Creamy Double Chorizo Linguine is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W32_UK_G11648-13273-9_add_ruccola_edit_Main_low-9b416f9b.jpg
